{"tid":1960928,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★突發！滙控倫敦股東大會只准董事要員出席 小股東試圖出席將被拒絕進場","createTime":"2020-04-06T12:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-23T11:40:24.000Z","uid":19454,"like":49,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e566d1f5b8f4a7fe13d8276ed53f38d356ee9eed","tid":1960928,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:29:32.000Z","msg":"滙控宣布，將於本月24日在倫敦舉行股東周年大會，不過基於英國政府實施社交距離措施，禁止非必要旅遊及公眾集會，今年股東將無法親身出席，試圖親身出席會議的人士將被拒絕進場。<br />\n<br />\n滙控指，為確保符合周年大會所需的法定人數及處理事務，只會由有限數目的董事及重要人員親身出席，而為確保投票獲得處理，股東只應委任大會主席為代表。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519181-20200406.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519181-20200406.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=IFfiXVp8wSeEFxWCfbiPLdArZVC5vK90EjT5EVN%2FGu4%3D&h=1fa39707\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1519181-20200406.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4bc89653\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1519181-20200406.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"a67251dd6efeb4bfcc83cebaa96b3bddf492e9a0","tid":1960928,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:29:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f257ffccec2dac39d40ca2b96d7cd904f0ed28","tid":1960928,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-06T12:30:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.g